(1. Executive Summary) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(This work adapted theFL_RANSOM_LLMrepository so that it could ingest and process a large) Tj
T*
(public CIC-IDS2018 CSV directly fromdata/wifi/raw/, transform it into an) Tj
T*
(anomaly-detection-as-language-modeling dataset, distribute benign training shards across) Tj
T*
(federated clients, train a LoRA-adapted SmolLM model, and evaluate the resulting) Tj
T*
(checkpoints on a balanced held-out set.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The refactor replaced the previous toy Wi-Fi logic, which was tied to two miniature CSV) Tj
T*
(files and synthetic fallback data, with a robust single-CSV processor capable of) Tj
T*
(detecting labels, preserving metadata such asTimestampandSrc IP, capping the effective) Tj
T*
(experiment size without touching the raw file, and preparing reproducible) Tj
T*
(train/test/tokenized artifacts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Additional engineering changes were applied to improve speed and server friendliness:) Tj
T*
(conservative multi-GPU parallel training, DataLoader worker controls, evaluation in) Tj
T*
(batches rather than one sample at a time, and delayed construction ofContentso that) Tj
T*
(textual conversion is performed only for the subset of flows effectively used in the) Tj
T*
(run.) Tj
T*
