T*
() Tj
T*
(The selected dataset isThuesday-20-02-2018_TrafficForML_CICFlowMeter.csv, from) Tj
T*
(CIC-IDS2018 processed traffic data for machine-learning algorithms. The operational) Tj
T*
(decision was to store the untouched dataset indata/wifi/raw/and to ensure that all) Tj
T*
(derived artifacts are created underdata/wifi/processed/. This preserves reproducibility,) Tj
T*
(keeps the raw source immutable, and makes it possible to reprocess the experiment at any) Tj
T*
(time from the same original file.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The download command used for the server, because theawsCLI was unavailable, was:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(wget -O data/wifi/raw/Thuesday-20-02-2018_TrafficForML_CICFlowMeter.csv) Tj
T*
("https://cse-cic-ids2018.s3.amazonaws.com/Processed%20Traffic%20Data%20for%20ML%20Algorithms/Thuesday-20-02-2018_TrafficForML_CICFlowMeter.csv") Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The raw file size observed on the server was approximately 3.8 GB. The first-line schema) Tj
T*
(validation confirmed 84 columns and the presence of the fields required by the new) Tj
T*
(processor, includingLabel,Timestamp,Src IP,Dst IP,Protocol,Flow Byts/s, andFlow) Tj
T*
(Duration.) Tj
