(Before the modifications described in this report, the Wi-Fi path in the repository was) Tj
T*
(not prepared for the CIC-IDS2018 Tuesday CSV. The pre-refactor processor expected two) Tj
T*
(small files namedbenign_wifi.csvandanomaly_wifi.csvindata/wifi/raw/, assumed a very) Tj
T*
(small tabular schema composed ofrssi,snr,latency, andthroughput, and could fabricate) Tj
T*
(fake rows if the files were missing or empty.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(That old behavior was useful only as a placeholder. It was not suitable for the real) Tj
T*
(CIC-IDS2018 schema, could not read a single large CSV, did not preserve operational) Tj
T*
(metadata needed by the new evaluator, and did not provide a mechanism to cap experiment) Tj
T*
(size cleanly without editing the raw dataset itself.) Tj
