(- Single-file loading.The processor resolvesraw_csv_filefrom the config and supports the) Tj
T*
(  CIC-IDS2018 CSV directly.) Tj
T*
(- Backward compatibility.The legacy pairbenign_wifi.csv+anomaly_wifi.csvis still) Tj
T*
(  accepted as a fallback mode.) Tj
T*
(- Robust label normalization.Text labels such asBenignand numeric0/1values are) Tj
