(- The benign training set is capped to 250,000 rows.) Tj
T*
(- The benign holdout is capped to 125,000 rows.) Tj
T*
(- The anomaly subset is capped to 125,000 rows.) Tj
T*
(- The final test set is the shuffled union of the benign holdout and anomaly cap.) Tj
T*
() Tj
