(7.3 GPU inventory) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(NVIDIA-SMI has failed because it couldn't communicate with the NVIDIA driver. Make sure) Tj
T*
(that the latest NVIDIA driver is installed and running.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The machine provides an Intel Core i9-13900K with 32 logical CPUs, 123 GiB of RAM, and) Tj
T*
(two NVIDIA RTX 4090 GPUs with 24 GiB each. Monitoring also showed that, prior to the) Tj
T*
(speed-oriented changes, the code underutilized both CPU and GPU resources, often keeping) Tj
T*
(most CPU threads idle while only partially engaging a single GPU.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(8. Performance Engineering Decisions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The tuning strategy followed a conservative philosophy appropriate for a multi-user) Tj
T*
(server:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- Use at most two GPUs because the machine physically has two, and because the) Tj
T*
(  experiment already uses exactly two clients.) Tj
T*
(- Limit DataLoader workers to four per process rather than aggressively using all CPUs.) Tj
T*
(- Keepbatch_size = 2for training to avoid unexpected VRAM pressure.) Tj
T*
(- Useeval_batch_size = 4with half precision to accelerate evaluation while keeping) Tj
T*
(  memory risk low on 24 GiB cards.) Tj
T*
(- Delay expensive text conversion until after caps are applied to the raw data.Important) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
