(  operational observation.The parallel training mode improved hardware utilization but) Tj
T*
(  did not reduce total training time for this relatively small experiment. The) Tj
T*
(  additional process launch and model-loading overhead outweighed the gain in raw) Tj
T*
(  compute. However, batched evaluation produced a much more meaningful speedup because) Tj
T*
(  the original evaluator was strongly serial.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
