T*
(| 2 | 0.8371 | 0.8640 | 22 | Fast loss drop indicates that the model quickly learned the benign-flow distribution.) Tj
T*
(| 3 | 0.6368 | 0.6999 | 21 | Training entered a more stable region with diminishing gains.) Tj
T*
(| 4 | 0.6569 | 0.6474 | 21 | Small oscillation, still within the same stability band.) Tj
T*
(| 5 | 0.5925 | 0.6257 | 22 | Lowest observed training losses, but evaluation did not improve materially beyond round 2.) Tj
T*
() Tj
