(15. Practical Guidance for Future Runs) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- If the objective is quick iteration, keep the current caps.) Tj
T*
(- If the objective is higher fidelity, raisebenign_train_capand possiblytest_*_cap, but) Tj
T*
(  be aware that preprocessing, tokenization, and evaluation time will grow.) Tj
T*
(- If VRAM becomes a concern, reduceeval_batch_sizefrom 4 to 2.) Tj
